{"tid":1916480,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【全民IP CAM】全民公衆cam，分區24小時通風報信救手足","createTime":"2020-03-09T01:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T17:49:35.000Z","uid":205733,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fe940624d36138890bb595e76a2cbcba727d96ec","tid":1916480,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"其實市面有咁多IP CAM, 只要大量手足裝CAM<br />\n各區對准所有18區所有屋苑 天台/公衆出入口<br />\n當區所有車的車 CAM<br />\n甚至對准埋...你懂的<br />\n然後分區/ 分屋苑/ 分編號公開提供 IP CAM 地址<br />\n我地就可以安在家中安全地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><ins><strong>24小時監測各區大廈出入口</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當有可疑人物於某屋苑出現，<br />\n立即於某區/某屋苑 telegram group 通知<br />\n聯絡埋當區區議員去屋苑<br />\n- 一來手足有時間準備<br />\n- 二來到時就有可能當面斷正<br />\n- 三來，如果成功錄低任何犯法野，即刻可以放出公海backup</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，希望有律師團隊可以幫手<br />\n覺得自己有危險既手足，可以每日可以向律師報平安<br />\n律師團隊可以輪班地監測<br />\n配合全民IP CAM，可以提前到達屋苑，保護手足<br />\n手足亦可以send 求救信號<br />\n就算真係被拉，都會知道係邊個<br />\n最起碼要做到唔會無命"},{"pid":"3cd7d6957734f77ceefb5ddaea839cb9c2ca2f76","tid":1916480,"uid":205733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"高科技抗暴"},{"pid":"133a13b723aa2d611eb929c231416289235cd465","tid":1916480,"uid":40250,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"唔好買hikvision d 大陸野"},{"pid":"df18b93d9fe43fc9eb3d822f7cca130caeecf2bf","tid":1916480,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:51:43.000Z","msg":"有無IT人幫下手？"},{"pid":"8b5d4f643a19135d08e3f40cd1a05dd8fc9f5293","tid":1916480,"uid":205733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"133a13b723aa2d611eb929c231416289235cd465","tid":1916480,"uid":40250,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"唔好買hikvision d 大陸野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:52:49.000Z","msg":"會送